LINUX
=====

Install basic development tools:
$ sudo apt-get install autoconf libtool build-essential libsigc++-2.0-dev libglib2.0-dev libpulse-dev libeigen3-dev libgles2-mesa-dev libpng12-dev

Copy missing sigc++config.h header file
sudo cp ../libsigcpp/libsigc++-2.2.10/sigc++config.h /usr/include/

Build and install libw
$ autoreconf -i; ./configure; sudo make install
